  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4555668">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4555668/" class="title-link">老头子们笑而不语</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4555668"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/48277547/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u48277547-9.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48277547/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">山九</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-12-30"
      class="main-meta">2010-12-30 13:08:40</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4555668_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这是作者在自己的小老头儿和老头儿时期，写给对当年事可以会心一笑的小老头和老头儿们看的，要的就是那一圈儿老头子笑而不语的效果，所以我们现在看起来并不好看。但是好玩儿。 不过这好玩儿也是怪苦涩，怪枯寂的。没什么笑点。 曹先生报人出身。说实在的……我看了几篇之后，...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4555668_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4555668_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1269508">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1269508/" class="title-link">与曹聚仁先生一起回忆民国往事</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1269508"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/button/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1178406-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/button/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">button</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-12-28"
      class="main-meta">2007-12-28 22:26:14</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1269508_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                     出于对民国历史的兴趣，最近在看听涛室人物谭这本书，也是第一次看曹聚仁先生的文集，此书是曹先生生前未完成的回忆录的一部分后由曹先生的女儿整理后出版。    这本书中都是有一些千字左右的闲适小文，讲述了邵力子老人如何为国共合作前后奔波，李宗仁、白崇禧、黄绍竑桂林...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1269508_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1269508_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评2篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
